"1136","Dear Shareholder,"
"1137","On January 11, 2010, the investment adviser to Wells Fargo Advantage Funds,"
"1138","Wells Fargo Funds Management, LLC (Funds Management), proposed to the Board of"
"1139","Trustees of Wells Fargo Advantage Funds, the mergers outlined in the table"
"1140","below. The Board of Trustees of Wells Fargo Advantage Funds approved the"
"1141","proposed mergers and the related Agreement and Plan of Reorganization, subject"
"1142","to the approval by shareholders of each Target Fund (shown in the table below)."
"1143","As a result, you are invited to vote on a proposal to merge your Target Fund"
"1144","into the corresponding Acquiring Fund (shown in the table below) (each, a"
"1145","Merger and together, the Mergers). The Board of Trustees of your Target Fund"
"1146","has unanimously approved the Merger and recommends that you vote FOR this"
"1147","proposal."
"1148","<TABLE>"
"1149","<CAPTION>"
