"1168","If approved by shareholders, this is a general summary of how each Merger will"
"1169","work:"
"1170","-     Each Target Fund will transfer all of its assets to the corresponding"
"1171","      Acquiring Fund."
"1172","-     Each Acquiring Fund will assume all of the liabilities of the"
"1173","      corresponding Target Fund."
"1174","-     Each Acquiring Fund will issue new shares that will be distributed to you"
"1175","      in an amount equal to the value of your Target Fund shares."
"1176","-     Each Target Fund shareholder would become a shareholder of the"
"1177","      corresponding Acquiring Fund and would have his or her investment managed"
"1178","      in accordance with the Acquiring Fund's investment strategies."
"1179","-     You will not incur any sales charges or similar transaction charges as a"
"1180","      result of the Merger."
"1181","-     It is expected that the Merger will be a non-taxable event for"
